</font></span></p><p style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; line-height: 14px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Thank you for completing your&nbsp;summer role&nbsp;<span style="line-height: 14px;">application for NCS with The Challenge</span><font style="line-height: 14px;">.</font></font></p><p style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><font><span style="line-height: 14px;">We have not&nbsp;</span></font><span style="line-height: 13.991477012634277px;">received</span><font style="line-height: 14px;">&nbsp;your care check information.&nbsp;</font></font></p><p style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; line-height: 14px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><b style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Care Check is the first step in the process to obtaining a full DBS (formerly CRB).</b><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">This process will be completed when a conditional job offer is made.</span></font></p><p style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; line-height: 14px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><font style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">If you already have a valid DBS (formerly known as CRB) <b>dated after 30 April 2013</b> please email a scanned copy through to&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font><a href="mailto:staffing.support@the-challenge.org" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">staffing.support@the-<u></u>challenge<wbr>.org</a></font></p><p style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; line-height: 14px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">If you do not have a current DBS please follow the instructions below.</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt; margin-bottom: 10.5pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><b>Please note you do not need to enter a password.&nbsp;</b><b><o:p></o:p></b></font></p><p style="font-size: 12pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;"></p><ol start="1" type="1" style="font-size: 12pt;"><li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 13.5pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Visit&nbsp;<a href="http://www.carecheck.co.uk/" target="_blank">www.carecheck.co.uk</a><o:p></o:p></font></li><li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 13.5pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Click on the&nbsp;<b>Applicant</b>&nbsp;tab<o:p></o:p></font></li><li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 13.5pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Please read all the notes and instructions<o:p></o:p></font></li><li class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="line-height: 18px;">Click on&nbsp;<b>Click here to continue to your application</b></span></font></li><li class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="line-height: 18px;">Go to&nbsp;<b>Disclosure and Barring Service (DBS) Application&nbsp;</b></span></font></li><li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 13.5pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Click on&nbsp;<b>Start Application</b><o:p></o:p></font></li><li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 13.5pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Enter the Organisation Reference:&nbsp;<b>evolutionrecruitment</b></font></li><li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 13.5pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><b style="line-height: 13.5pt; text-indent: -18pt;">You do not need a password,&nbsp;</b><span style="line-height: 13.5pt; text-indent: -18pt;">press enter to continue with your application&nbsp;</span></font></li><li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 13.5pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Enter your personal information to apply for the DBS.</font></li></ol><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" size="2"><span style="line-height: 18px;"><div><b style="font-family: arial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">N.B You will be asked to upload your documents if and when you are offered a role.</b></div><div><b style="font-family: arial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></b></div>Thank you for taking the time to complete the Care Check. You will be notified when this process is complete<font size="3">.</font></span></font><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="line-height: 17.98611068725586px;"><br></span></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="line-height: 17.98611068725586px;">Warm Regards,<br></span></font><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="line-height: 18px;">{!Contact.OwnerFullName}</span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="line-height: 18px;">t:&nbsp;{!Contact.OwnerPhone}</span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="line-height: 18px;">e:&nbsp;{!Contact.Contact_Owner_alternative_email__c}</span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="line-height: 18px;">The Challenge&nbsp;</span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="line-height: 18px;"><br></span></font></div><div><div style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="line-height: 18px;">Please Note:-</span></font></div><div style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);">We employ a 